#: addons/ui-inspector.wad/addon:3 input:6 standard
msgid ""
"This utility allows add-on designers to inspect the structure, hierarchy, "
"and properties of panels and windows. This allows you to obtain the internal "
"names of panels and mimic existing windows without searching their source "
"code, and assists with troubleshooting misbehaving plugins."
msgstr ""

